<name>Dynamic Pathfinding and Adaptive Switching Agent</name>
<motivation>
This approach aims to enhance the agent's ability to navigate through KA59 by dynamically adapting to the game state using advanced pathfinding techniques and strategic switching between selectable pieces. By refining the A* pathfinding algorithm to better handle obstacles and utilizing heuristic hints provided in the state, the agent can make more informed decisions about movement. Additionally, the implementation of strategic switching between selectable pieces will increase flexibility and adaptability, allowing the agent to overcome complex scenarios and maximize progress through levels.
</motivation>
